data.title: "Verbotene Liebe" Episode #1.3705 (TV Episode 2010)
data.meta_description: Episode #1.3705: Directed by Kerstin Krause. With Wolfram Grandezka, Jens Hartwig, Jana Schölermann, Stephan Käfer. Philipp tirelessly helps Nicola trough her guilt trip, even finds on her photographs a tattoo on the stabber's arm. The stumble upon Oscar, who has one just like it, but is afraid to betray his (street gang?) mate. Ansgar keeps lying in jail, even to his defense counsel, and turning Sebastian away. Andi and Helena get a surprise going send-off party.
